name: gridAggregationLookupSelector
description: Get the aggregation results as a lookup.

name: gridAggregationModelSelector
description:
Get the aggregation model, containing the aggregation function of each column.
If a column is not in the model, it is not aggregated.

name: gridColumnDefinitionsSelector
description: Get an array of column definitions in the order rendered on screen..

name: gridColumnFieldsSelector
description: Get an array of column fields in the order rendered on screen.

name: gridColumnLookupSelector
description: Get the columns as a lookup (an object containing the field for keys and the definition for values).

name: gridColumnPositionsSelector
description: Get the left position in pixel of each visible columns relative to the left of the first column.

name: gridColumnVisibilityModelSelector
description:
Get the column visibility model, containing the visibility status of each column.
If a column is not registered in the model, it is visible.

name: gridColumnsStateSelector
description: Get the columns state

name: gridColumnsTotalWidthSelector
description: Get the summed width of all the visible columns.

name: gridEditRowsStateSelector
description: Select the row editing state.

name: gridExpandedRowCountSelector
description: Get the amount of rows accessible after the filtering process.

name: gridExpandedSortedRowEntriesSelector
description:
Get the id and the model of the rows accessible after the filtering process.
Does not contain the collapsed children.

name: gridExpandedSortedRowIdsSelector
description:
Get the id of the rows accessible after the filtering process.
Does not contain the collapsed children.

name: gridFilterModelSelector
description: Get the current filter model.

name: gridFilterableColumnDefinitionsSelector
description: Get the filterable columns as an array.

name: gridFilterableColumnLookupSelector
description: Get the filterable columns as a lookup (an object containing the field for keys and the definition for values).

name: gridFilteredDescendantRowCountSelector
description: Get the amount of descendant rows accessible after the filtering process.

name: gridFilteredRowCountSelector
description:
Get the amount of rows accessible after the filtering process.
Includes top level and descendant rows.

name: gridFilteredSortedRowEntriesSelector
description:
Get the id and the model of the rows accessible after the filtering process.
Contains the collapsed children.

name: gridFilteredSortedRowIdsSelector
description:
Get the id of the rows accessible after the filtering process.
Contains the collapsed children.

name: gridFilteredSortedTopLevelRowEntriesSelector
description: Get the id and the model of the top level rows accessible after the filtering process.

name: gridFilteredTopLevelRowCountSelector
description: Get the amount of top level rows accessible after the filtering process.

name: gridPageCountSelector
description: Get the amount of pages needed to display all the rows if the pagination is enabled

name: gridPageSelector
description: Get the index of the page to render if the pagination is enabled

name: gridPageSizeSelector
description: Get the maximum amount of rows to display on a single page if the pagination is enabled

name: gridPaginatedVisibleSortedGridRowEntriesSelector
description: Get the id and the model of each row to include in the current page if the pagination is enabled.

name: gridPaginatedVisibleSortedGridRowIdsSelector
description: Get the id of each row to include in the current page if the pagination is enabled.

name: gridPaginationMetaSelector
description: Get the pagination meta

name: gridPaginationModelSelector
description: Get the pagination model

name: gridPaginationRowCountSelector
description: Get the row count

name: gridPaginationRowRangeSelector
description: Get the index of the first and the last row to include in the current page if the pagination is enabled.

name: gridPinnedColumnsSelector
description: Get the visible pinned columns model.

name: gridQuickFilterValuesSelector
description: Get the current quick filter values.

name: gridRowIdSelector
description: Get the row id for a given row

name: gridSortModelSelector
description: Get the current sorting model.

name: gridSortedRowEntriesSelector
description: Get the id and the model of the rows after the sorting process.

name: gridSortedRowIdsSelector
description: Get the id of the rows after the sorting process.

name: gridVirtualizationColumnEnabledSelector
description: Get the enabled state for column virtualization

name: gridVirtualizationEnabledSelector
description: Get the enabled state for virtualization

name: gridVirtualizationRowEnabledSelector
description: Get the enabled state for row virtualization

name: gridVirtualizationSelector
description: Get the columns state

name: gridVisibleColumnDefinitionsSelector
description: Get the visible columns as a lookup (an object containing the field for keys and the definition for values).

name: gridVisibleColumnFieldsSelector
description: Get the field of each visible column.

name: gridVisiblePinnedColumnDefinitionsSelector
description: Get the visible pinned columns.

name: gridVisibleRowsSelector
returnType: { rows: GridRowEntry<GridValidRowModel>[]; range: { firstRowIndex: number; lastRowIndex: number } | null; rowIdToIndexMap: Map<GridRowId, number> }
description:
Get the rows, range and rowIndex lookup map after filtering and sorting.
Does not contain the collapsed children.
